short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds console.sparkline to all web pages and Chrome Devtools.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: console.sparkline() is a chrome devtools extension that adds a tool similar to console.log(), but that renders arrays of numbers as little inline sparkline images for you. Great for quickly visualizing time series you encounter while you are hacking on something.
